    "name": "Midnight Alert",
    "steam_appid": 2242090,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>一款考验你技能的恐怖FPS游戏在这里。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242090/extras/9b4202deabc3144731b3f58c60c097f9.avif?t=1754521511\" width=616 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一位神父决定举行一个会打开地狱之门并带来混乱的仪式；问题是，他的计划成功了，现在我们必须在这个生物和人类无法共存的新世界中为生命而战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >到处都是生物</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >保持警惕，因为生物可能会从任何方向出现。准备好你的枪并保护自己。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >恐怖气氛</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >得到一把枪来保护自己免受他们的生物伤害并不意味着你就不必担心周围的恐怖。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这款游戏旨在营造一种黑暗气氛，并提供良好的恐怖游戏体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这些生物偶尔也会让你吓一跳。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >紧张的游戏玩法和老板战</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242090/extras/2b1ad9492d73abba7e91cf8789159351.avif?t=1754521511\" width=616 height=400 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏中，你必须与多个生物以及具有挑战性的老板战斗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好迎接任何事情。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >噩梦模式</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242090/extras/be21735e17620a24bfcf273f0eebe746.avif?t=1754521511\" width=616 height=206 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你够勇敢，你可以尝试噩梦模式，没有保存点，生物更强大。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >武器自定义</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242090/extras/7326653fb167c712fda71573fb657f38.avif?t=1754521511\" width=616 height=316 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在你的旅途中，你可以找到一些武器模组，让你自定义你的武器。你可以更改颜色，附加或拆卸模组、消声器、激光、手电筒、子弹扩展器、瞄准镜等。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >与对象互动</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以与物体互动并找到一些有趣的东西。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >质量设置</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以根据你的显卡选择一系列选项以获得更好的体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >还支持4k分辨率甚至更大。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >键位映射和控制器支持</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2242090/extras/78fd912814683b60ebfaa2f5bfd8de7c.avif?t=1754521511\" width=616 height=316 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以重新映射键位以匹配你的偏好，并使用控制器来提升你的游戏体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以试验相机灵敏度以微调并改善你的瞄准。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多重保存和加载</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以开始自己的旅程，并在不失去之前所做的一切的情况下重新开始。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次游戏都可能不同。</p>",
